				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/D%C6%B0-d%C4%A9-s%E1%BB%B1-h%E1%BB%87-Ng%E1%BB%B1-s%E1%BB%AD-%C4%91%C3%A0i-ng%E1%BB%A5c-ng%E1%BB%A5c-l%E1%BA%A1i-s%E1%BA%A3o-ki%E1%BA%BFn-x%C3%A2m-t%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1c-b%E1%BA%A5t-n%C4%83ng-kham-t%E1%BB%AD-ng%E1%BB%A5c-trung-b%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-nh%E1%BA%A5t/poem-_EqKDCRtfaF59WZkjTMkvQ">Dư dĩ sự hệ Ngự sử đài ngục, ngục lại sảo kiến xâm, tự đạc bất năng kham, tử ngục trung, bất đắc nhất biệt Tử Do, cố tác nhị thi thụ ngục tốt Lương Thành, dĩ di Tử Do kỳ 2 - 予以事繫禦史台獄獄吏稍見侵，自度不能堪，死獄中，不得一別子由，故作二詩授獄卒梁成，以遺子由其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-K%E1%BB%B3/%C4%90%E1%BB%89nh-Minh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-tb-mZVQzlQRzQhoKGz3MrQ">Đỉnh Minh tự - 鼎銘寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-K%E1%BB%B3/author-w6Nzdd7lvpiIacUaKAMQvw">Nguyễn Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Long-C%C3%A1t/L%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1-th%E1%BB%8D/poem-1E92UYOAaxLx1lwJiWgKKA">Lục thập tự thọ - 六十自壽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Long-C%C3%A1t/author-VISrZKXHGNu9v2YwwCwG_g">Nguyễn Long Cát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tam-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-WtpSIybVDDgZfBbWafn_OQ">Tam tuyệt cú kỳ 1 - 三絕句其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%B7ng-n%E1%BB%99i-I/poem-UL7Xr5cf7JCmvHBE7R8uHA">Tặng nội (I) - 贈內（I）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Th%C3%A1i-H%C3%A0ng-l%E1%BB%99/poem-7VaC8RXuJ80PZ9SXfvj-vg">Thái Hàng lộ - 太行路</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/T%E1%BB%8Bch-th%E1%BB%A9-Chi-Ngh%C4%A9a-d%E1%BB%8Bch-v%C3%A3n-L%E1%BA%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-hi%E1%BB%87p-tr%E1%BA%A5n-T%C3%B4-Xuy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BA%A7u/poem-_W0oNSCYrVyuJaeugHf8bA">Tịch thứ Chi Nghĩa dịch, vãn Lạng Sơn hiệp trấn Tô Xuyên hầu - 夕佽芝義驛挽諒山協鎮蘇川侯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%99i-xu%E1%BA%A5t/poem-SURrVypCme4I6f33jiLrgA">Tội xuất - 罪出</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-M_NlL2QYyIpgu5vZrvAs8w">Triệu Mạnh Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%8Bch/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-thi-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-03/poem-NZlr6VQcoCsQNGztn_dQ0g">Vịnh hoài thi (ngũ ngôn) kỳ 03 - 詠懷詩（五言）其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%8Bch/author-iqPFGu2O2IWkMRslgHjtDw">Nguyễn Tịch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C3%B4-gia-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-Lmk1srGEtNuIi0hYAVvAPA">Vô gia biệt - 無家別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
